node.text: The Bailsmen bring some love back into the house ❤️

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Dante NYC on September 15, 2021 tagging @godslovenyc, and @stevefreihon. May be an image of drink and text that says 'CAFF ANTE'.

node.text:
We’re thrilled to announce that our signature Negroni Sessions are officially back. We’re offering 11 Negronis, all at $10 between 3pm and 5pm daily. $1 from every one sold will be donated to our dear friends @godslovenyc . Swipe ➡️ to see the menu.

Why 11 Negronis? That’s the number of cocktails we reopened with back in 2015. Incredibly we’re close to 60 rotating, seasonal drinks today. 

Looking forward to serving you ❤️

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Dante NYC on September 15, 2021 tagging @godslovenyc, and @stevefreihon. May be an image of drink and text that says 'CAFF ANTE'.
Photo shared by Dante NYC on September 15, 2021 tagging @campariamerica, and @negroniweek. May be an image of text.

Photo by Dante NYC in Sydney, Australia with @lindenpride, @capitan_campari, @simonfordsgin, @negroniweek, @fordsgin, @chefneilperry, @campariaustria, and @margaretdoublebay. May be an image of drink and indoor.

node.text:
Dante NYC in Sydney!

We’re thrilled to offer a selection from our Negroni Sessions this @negroniweek in Sydney Australia at @chefneilperry ‘s awesome new restaurant @margaretdoublebay 🇦🇺🇺🇸

Available this week from Wednesday through Sunday! We’re donating to @hopedeliverysydney with proceeds from the sales of the cocktails.

Thank you to @campariau and @fordsgin for their incredible support ❤️

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Dante NYC on September 13, 2021 tagging @rodrigooleme, @chefjgv, @lindenpride, @massimobottura, @dbldzl, @chefjoseandres, @wckitchen, @chefneilperry, @sanpellegrino_us, @forsythia_nyc, and @mariocarbone. May be an image of food, drink and indoor.

node.text:
We are celebrating Negroni Week with a limited-edition “Chef’s Menu” featuring Negroni recipes from some of dear friends and chefs from across the globe. 

For each of the “Chef’s Menu” cocktails sold, Dante & @sanpellegrino_us will donate $10 to World Central Kitchen, Jose Andres’ charity feeding the victims of Hurricane Ida in New Orleans. 

BRONZE from The Bazaar Meat by Jose Andres and Miguel Lancha (Fords Gin, Martínez Lacuesta Blanc Vermouth, Tempus Fugit L’Aero D’Or Kina and Cynar)

NEGRONI IN EMILIA from Torno Subito by Massimo Bottura and Bernardo Paladino (Cherry-infused Gin Mare, Campari, Vermouth Mancino rosso amaranto, Tradizionale Balsamic vinegar and Cherry essence spray)

GOLD’N SBAGLIATO from Carbone by Mario Carbone, Rich Torrisi and Jeff Zalaznick (Quinquina Aperitif, Martini Ambrato, Strega, Sancerre, San Pellegrino, Lemon Bitters and Verjus)

AUSTRALIAN BUSH NEGRONI from Margaret by Neil Perry (Green ant gin, Davidson plum aperitivo, wattleseed vermouth)

JG’s NEGRONI from Jean-Georges (don Fulano, antica formula, st agrestis, grapefruit)

Alongside our favorite bar snack, the incredible SUPPLI from the wonders of @forsythia_nyc . Available this week only!

❤️

May be an image of indoor and text that says '2013 La Factoría COCHUE ARTESANAL COMES TO DANTE NEW YORK CITY AUGUST 16TH TO 18TH 2PM 6PM'.

node.text:
Dante is thrilled to announce our first residency of 2021, hosting our dear friends from Puerto Rico’s legendary cocktail bar @lafactoriapr 🇵🇷❤️. 

Factoría bartenders Carlos Irizarry and Gigi Temprano will join Dante’s Head Bartender Bar Eloy Pacheco to bring local Caribbean flavors in a selection of tropical rum-based cocktails from @bacardiusa . Cuban performer Chino Ponds will play a variety of Latin music for all three days of the pop-up, from 2:00pm daily.

$2 from each cocktail sold will be donated directly to @prcocktailweek Tip Jar, an emergency fund established to help support the local Puerto Rican hospitality industry impacted by the closures of bars and restaurants due to the COVID-19 pandemic.

Monday Aug 16 through Wednesday Aug 18 from 3pm til 6pm during BCB at Caffe Dante, Macdougal street.

Reservations available through RESY. We can’t wait to host you ❤️
